text: Radosava Kočanović (born 11 November 1994) is a Montenegrin footballer who plays as a midfielder for 1. ŽFL club ŽFK Breznica. She has officially played for the senior Montenegro women's national team. ==International career== Kočanović capped for Montenegro at senior level during the 2015 FIFA Women's World Cup qualification – UEFA Group 6, in a 0–10 home loss to England on 17 September 2014. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Montenegrin women's footballers Category:Montenegro women's international footballers Category:ŽFK Breznica players
